"This watch has given me a significant control over my phone over the past month I’ve had a chance to use it. It give me up-to-minute notifications, so there’s no need to constantly check my phone; a remote for all my apps at the flick of a wrist. I don’t have any service pertaining to its cellular features, so I have no means of reviewing it, being on Metro Wireless. The rotator crown is very receptive and precise, as well, with unnoticeable signs of wearing.\nWithout it, however, I’ve had no trouble with using it as a secondary means of answering calls and messages; even from apps such as Facebook Messenger. Still scared to test it’s waterproof capabilities, but sweat during exercise has never been an issue. All it requires is a good, consistent, clean swipe"